1. *Zaboravila* je da će biti u školi u 9h (She forgot that she would be in school at 9am).
2. Ona se *zaboravila* u njegovim očima (She got lost in his eyes).
3. *Zaboravila* sam da pripremim ukusan ručak (I forgot to prepare a delicious lunch).
4. Ono što je *zaboravila* je da ona nije sama (What she forgot was that she is not alone).
5. Da li si *zaboravila* da smo dogovorili da ideš u bioskop? (Did you forget that we agreed that you would go to the movies?).
6. *Zaboravila* je čitavu situaciju (She forgot the whole situation).